title: [Urudwek's Weaponry]
[Urudwek's Combat Gear]
description: A decorative linden branch wreath hangs on one of the chipped red brick walls, and a painted nightscape ceiling rises overhead.  A verdant elderberry bush sits in one corner of a buffed cherrywood floor.  There is a small brown box on one side of the shop and a large oak table on the other.
